com.stormpath.sdk.saml

Interface AuthnVerificationRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Resource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultAuthnVerificationRequest

    public interface AuthnVerificationRequest
extends Resource
    An AuthnVerificationRequest encapsulates the fields of a SAML AuthnRequest targeted against a particular Stormpath Application.
    Since:
    1.3.0
